sitan\n* [[Korel Cezayirli]] as Metin \u00d6\u011fretmen\n* [[Murat Ayd\u0131n]] as Fezo\n* [[Ozan Erdo\u011fan]] as Tav\u015fan\n* [[Muhammet Cang\u00f6ren]] as Allahyar\n* [[Levent Uzunbilek]] as Mirza\n* [[\u0130srafil Parlak]] as Ad\u0131be\u015f\n* [[Havin Funda Sa\u00e7]] as Esme\n\n== Release ==\n=== General release ===\nThe film opened in 133 screens across Turkey on {{start date|2009|04|17}} at number seven in the Turkish box office chart with an opening weekend gross of $99,761.<ref name=\"BOM01\">{{cite web |title=Deli Deli Olma |first= |last= |coauthors= |url=http://www.boxofficemojo.com/movies/intl/?id=_fDELIDELIOLMA01&country=TR&wk=2009W16&id=_fDELIDELIOLMA01&p=.htm |work=Box Office Mojo |date= |accessdate=2010-02-24 }}</ref>\n\n=== Festival screenings ===\n* 2009\n**[[Sinema Burada Film Festival]]<ref name=\"TZ01\" />\n**[[46th Antalya Golden Orange Film Festival]]<ref name=\"TZ03\">{{cite web|title=Emerging directors dominate Golden Orange competition|url=http://www.todayszaman.com/tz-web/news-187182-emerging-directors-dominate-golden-orange-competition.html|work=Today's Zaman|accessdate=2010-02-24|url-status=dead|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140429080652/http://www.todayszaman.com/tz-web/news-187182-emerging-directors-dominate-golden-orange-competition.html|archivedate=2014-04-29}}</ref>\n**[[4th Bursa International Silk Road Film Festival]]<ref name=\"BISRFF01\">{{cite web |title=Deli Deli Olma / Piano Girl |url=http://ipekyolufilmfest.com/webeng/habduy.aspx?id=92&tip=FILM2 |work=BISRFF |accessdate=2010-02-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110713053247/http://ipekyolufilmfest.com/webeng/habduy.aspx?id=92&tip=FILM2 |archive-date=2011-07-13 |url-status=dead }}</ref><ref name=\"TZ04\">{{cite web|title=10 titles vying for prizes at Bursa\u2019s Silk Road festival|url=http://www.todayszaman.com/tz-web/news-191436-10-titles-vying-for-prizes-at-bursas-silk-road-festival.html|work=Today's Zaman|accessdate=2010-02-24|url-status=dead|